---
title: HelloHero: Chermoula-Spiced Roast Lamb with Cheesy Garlic Veggie Crush, Radish Slaw & Balsamic Glaze
description: You might need a pair of sunglasses for this meal because it’s blinding, especially with garlic, potato and carrot combined into a sunset veggie crush. What goes better with veggies than a lamb roast of course, and this one is succulent, tender and drizzled in a rich balsamic sauce. Trust us, it tastes just as good as it looks.

